
Personal Commands
look:: repeats the long form room description
look at <feature or object>:: examine an object or feature more closely
take <object> :: add an object to your inventory
drop <object> :: drop and object into the current room
inventory :: display your current inventory

Travel Commands
Use any of the following commands to travel within the game
go <direction>::
go <room name>::
<direction>::
<room name>::

Game Commmands
savegame:: save your current progress (*only one save file)
loadgame:: load your game from an existing save